comments: Ennis III (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position on Leonard (LAC) at the end of the drive and Ross (ORL) cleanly intercepts his intended pass.
Kennard (LAC) commits a take foul on Ross (ORL).
Carter-Williams (ORL) reaches in and makes contact to Leonard's (LAC) arm and body, which causes him to temporarily lose control of the ball.
Zubac (LAC) is deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Ennis III (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Jackson (LAC) and Carter Jr. (ORL) cleanly blocks the shot.
After Okeke (ORL) retrieves the rebound, Jackson (LAC) makes hand on ball contact to cleanly dislodge the ball.
Carter Jr. (ORL) makes marginal contact with Leonard's (LAC) legal bent arm in the post and the contact does not affect his ability to defend.
During the rebound, Ennis III (ORL) and Jackson (LAC) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Jackson (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Ennis III (ORL).

Leonard (LAC) legally contests Carter Jr.'s (ORL) tip attempt at the basket, and marginal contact occurs to Carter Jr.'s arm after the release that does not affect his ability to follow-through naturally during his play at the basket.
Mann (LAC) passes the ball inbounds within 5 seconds.
Okeke (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position on Batum (LAC) at the end of the drive and makes clean ball contact to deflect the pass.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Jacksons (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs as they engage and disengage.
Carter Jr. (ORL) cleanly blocks the shot attempt and makes incidental "high-five" contact with Mann (LAC) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Zubac (LAC) is deemed to be in the lane for about three seconds when the shot is imminent.
During the rebound, Okeke (ORL) and Zubac (LAC) both make clean ball contact and the ball lands on Mann (LAC) out of bounds.
Mann (LAC) extends two arms out and makes contact to Carter-Williams' (ORL) arm and body before any ball contact and a take foul is correctly whistled.
Leonard (LAC) commits a take foul on Carter-Williams (ORL).

Mann (LAC) is airborne when he gains control of the ball and his right foot comes down first, which he establishes as his pivot. He then lifts and re-plants his pivot foot prior to releasing his pass.
From all available angles, it appears Leonard (LAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Carter Jr. (ORL) after he secured the rebound.
Leonard (LAC) inadvertently dribbles the ball off of Ennis III's (ORL) legally planted leg and Carter-Williams (ORL) cleanly retrieves the loose ball.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Jackson (LAC) throws an errant inbounds pass that goes out of bounds and Porter Jr. (ORL) avoids making contact to the ball.
Leonard (LAC) commits a take foul on Ross (ORL).
